 the mortgage services", "bbox": [204.2, 1057.1, 1111.0, 1078.0]}, {"text": "business are reported as a discontinued operation for the year ended December 31, 2014 and for all prior", "bbox": [204.2, 1082.1, 1075.7, 1103.0]}, {"text": "periods presented. As necessary, the amounts have been retroactively adjusted in all periods presented to", "bbox": [204.2, 1107.1, 1078.3, 1128.0]}, {"text": "give recognition to the discontinued operations. See Note 10 of our consolidated financial statements", "bbox": [204.2, 1132.1, 1046.8, 1153.0]}, {"text": "included in this annual report on Form 10-K.", "bbox": [204.2, 1157.1, 578.5, 1178.0]}, {"text": "(3)", "bbox": [162.5, 1195.6, 186.8, 1216.4]}, {"text": "EBITDA is the financial measure which management uses to evaluate the performance of our segments.", "bbox": [204.2, 1195.6, 1073.9, 1216.4]}, {"text": "“EBITDA” is defined as net income before interest expense, provision for income taxes, depreciation and", "bbox": [204.2, 1220.6, 1086.2, 1241.4]}, {"text": "amortization of fixed and intangible assets. Because EBITDA is calculated from net income, this", "bbox": [204.2, 1245.6, 1012.7, 1266.4]}, {"text": "presentation includes EBITDA from discontinued operations of our mortgage services business. In addition,", "bbox": [204.2, 1270.6, 1107.1, 1291.4]}, {"text": "this Management’s Discussion and Analysis includes references to EBITDA margin, which is computed as", "bbox": [204.2, 1295.6, 1097.7, 1316.4]}, {"text": "EBITDA divided by revenues from continuing and discontinued operations. See Note 18 of our consolidated", "bbox": [204.2, 1320.6, 1111.8, 1341.4]}, {"text": "financial statements included in this annual report on Form 10-K.", "bbox": [204.2, 1345.6, 750.3, 1366.4]}, {"text": "Although EBITDA is a non-GAAP financial measure, EBITDA is frequently used by securities analysts,", "bbox": [204.2, 1384.0, 1079.2, 1404.8]}, {"text": "lenders and others in their evaluation of companies, EBITDA has limitations as an analytical tool, and", "bbox": [204.2, 1409.0, 1056.9, 1429.8]}, {"text": "should not be considered in isolation, or as a substitute for an analysis of our results of operations or cash", "bbox": [204.2, 1434.0, 1083.1, 1454.8]}, {"text": "32", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}